*FvwmPagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk1, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
*FvwmPagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk2, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
*FvwmPagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk3, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 4, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
